-- Brookfield May Buy Hammerson London Offices, Property Week Says
-- B y   S i m o n   P a c k a r d
-- 2012-06-15T09:32:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-15/brookfield-may-buy-hammerson-london-offices-property-week-says.html
Brookfield Office Properties Inc. (BPO)  is
in exclusive talks to acquire  Hammerson Plc (HMSO) ’s London office
portfolio for more than 500 million pounds ($777 million),
 Property Week  reported, citing people with knowledge of the
negotiations.  The exclusivity period ends June 22. Brookfield is
acquiring 13 properties, including Hammerson’s development
sites, the magazine reported.  No one was immediately available to comment on the report
at Hammerson or at New York-based Brookfield.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simon Packard in London at 
 packard@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net  